description:
Extreme Speed Track Event - Club4AG Discounted Entry Fee
For SATURDAY DECEMBER 7th 2013


Registration: Buttonwillow Raceway 12/07/2013 ( Saturday ) (Dec 7, 2013)
BUTTONWILLOW RACEWAY

Arrival time: 7:00am-8:00am

Join us!!

name: RS-R Sports-i Full Coilover System for Scion FR-S/ Subaru BRZ
description:
Moto Spec Sportsi coilovers tuned to Moto Miwa's preferences for the best ride on the street and performance on the track.

Recommended height: 
Front -25 to -30mm 
Rear -25 to -30mm 

Maximum adjustment range: 
Front +15mm to -40mm 
Rear +30mm to -80mm 

Recommended adjustment range: 
Front +5 to -40mm 
Rear 0 to -50mm

Spring rate: 
Front 6.00kg/mm 
Rear 7.00kg/mm

Dampers are 36 way adjustable in the front, and 24 way adjustable in the rear.

Double-Tap lower brackets to allow height change without relocating piston position or altering spring preload.

name: ChargeSpeed "Bottom Line" Body Enhancement 5 Piece Splitter Kit
description:
Charge Speed uses the finest 1x1 weave carbon fiber and fine-thread FRP on all products made in Japan.  

ChargeSpeed Bottom Line lower splitter 5 piece set

CARBON FIBER $2250
or
Fiber Resin FRP $1750

Japan's premier carbon fiber body panel manufacturer releases another lineup, The Bottom Line lower splitter kit, available for the Scion FRS/Toyota 86.

The kit is also available for the Subaru BRZ, with it's own specific front bumper lower dam design.

Single 1x1 fine weave carbon lines up very precisely along the seams, and the fit and finish are one of the best in the industry.

For 2013, we chose this for the Club4AG Scion FR-S to give a fresh look, and to demonstrate the master craftsmen's manufacturing capability of carbon and FRP body extension.


Available for Scion FR-S and Subaru BRZ, please specify as front splitter is different between the two cars.  

This Carbon Fiber or FRP lower body splitter set contains 
- Front Lower Splitter
- 2 side splitters (left and right)
- 2 rear splitters (left and right)

The Bottom Line splitter set attaches exactly to the shape of the bumper and side rails, and with 3M adhesive tape and expansion clips or tapping screws(hardware and tape not included).   Minimum drilling required for secure fit.  Qualified Professional installation is required for warranty, and we will not accept returns on modified or altered units.  

This is the same kit used on the Club4AG FR-S and RJ DeVerra's Scion Tuner Challenge cars.

name: Club4AG version Scion FR-S Guage Cluster Overlay Kit (white)
description:
These are quality made in Japan overly cluster kit for Scion FR-S which simply covers the original cluster backing and adds our logo on white base with Toyota "T-Mesh" pattern.

It takes about 1 hour DIY installation time, and are made to order with approximately 2 weeks turn-around time.
 Manufactured by Cyberstork in Japan, they are printed on high grade PET laminates with UV high resolution printing process.

* These will not work on Subaru BRZ, and are applicable to USA market clusters with MPH indicators and not for KM/H indicator outside market vehicles.  This due to the way these must retain the original backing of the cluster and all indicator markings must match in shape and size with the overlay.  Supplied with both manual transmission and semi-automatic paddle shift transmission cluster panel inserts.

* This does not include a gauge cluster, it is designed to modify your own cluster unit.  Please be sure to take precautions with installation as we cannot warranty the gauge cluster if damaged in the installation process.

*Actual production unit will have a TPMS (Tire Pressure Warning Lamp) on the cluster with option to black it out at the owner's discretion.  (Not responsible for any tire failure or induced damages...and provided only for those who go racing and want to not see that thing blinking all day when we change tires and pressures all day on the cars)

(Limited Time offer) You will get a bonus Club4AG Blue emblem set for initial 10 customers.
